{"tid":1550373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，你地醒未","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T16:52:54.000Z","uid":164152,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"36ecdd0a68ace375b610c1d2d2cd4384c0d2a6c6","tid":1550373,"uid":164152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:45:48.000Z","msg":"去撚到今時今日<br />\n<br />\n見証著呢班藍屍同死黑警每日做盡壞事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">搞尻良心小店<br />\n任由黑社會無差別攻擊市民<br />\n任意向示威者開槍<br />\n男警搜女人身<br />\n新屋嶺<br />\n太子手足<br />\n各種不同形式嘅被自殺</span></span><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母完全不能盡錄<br />\n你地仲唔肯升級武力？<br />\n仲要攬住所謂嘅「民意」同「道德高地」？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算唔係主動打班黑警，見到有手足比人拉緊嗰陣點解冇人幫手救？<br />\n喂比著我係班黑警，見到你地咁撚淆底，一出動向前行幾步你地就退，我仲洗驚你班撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">醒下啦你地！仲要有幾多手足比人拉比人姦比人殺你地先識醒覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"4b80d069e5f776d069eab5af7aaa6ceae047e7c4","tid":1550373,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:46:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9de71cd8f68c8ca921ccf69fd021db79bd6fd17","tid":1550373,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:46:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b798636aeb49f983eb31dead98d0599d5ec72579","tid":1550373,"uid":164152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:46:47.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3e80815682f1ed62b2f18458d775ef9229eabeaf","tid":1550373,"uid":85803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:47:14.000Z","msg":"仲要保護藍絲 保護行兇者<br />\n任由左膠阻住晒<br />\n#冷氣分化撚here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac20b9b6b60fb89936d084c1d921fdad0f2f3dd","tid":1550373,"uid":240608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:49:07.000Z","msg":"宜家無理到民意<br />\n<br />\n係裝備差太遠。身材武力差太遠<br />\n佢地有受過訓練<br />\n<br />\n好單簡 淨係朝早 東涌 查車，成堆差佬搜你<br />\n你做到d 乜。 眼白白睇住個女仔比人搜<br />\n<br />\n你以後去邊到集會 查車都要任人魚肉，點反抗？"},{"pid":"b680e615f00ae78e66ed9952f6485c11c91b52fc","tid":1550373,"uid":164152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit